  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&#x2022;	Provision of Agricultural tools (shovels, hoes, cutlasses, watering can, rake to 85 Bbola survivors in Bo district  
&#x2022;	Provision of Seeds (rice, cassava, potatoes, groundnuts and green vegetables) to 85 Bbola survivors in Kenema district 

&#x2022;	Provision of livestock, male and female goats as well as hens and cockerels
&#x2022;	Provision of technical support/training  in basic Agronomic practices 
&#x2022;	Provide vertenary service and  check-up for livestock  
&#x2022;	Training in basic animal husbandry</narrative>
  </description>
